title: Lactate build-up in aquatic animals during dives 2

content.question: Describe the most likely shape of the curve if blood oxygen levels of Weddell seals were plotted rather than blood lactate levels. Include in your description the likely shape of the curve between 0 and 20 minutes and the shape of the curve after 20 minutes.
